704176f-b.title: Brooklyn: Fillmore Avenue - Marine Parkway
704176f-b.text:
Tillmore Aenue, west from Marine Parkway, showing
a W. P. A. highway project. The houses seen in the right
background are on Stuart Street and those in the left back-
gTOund are on Brown Street. View 2 shows another section
of the project.
August 13, 1935
Views 1,2
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroghs Project
